{"tid":2070880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共：反對台灣為港人提供庇護 引入反共分子禍害台灣民眾","createTime":"2020-06-19T12:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T19:59:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":163,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e33d007389a7477bcab3b73671d8bb150d35c0","tid":2070880,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"國台辦：台灣香港人道援助關懷行動只會禍害台灣民眾<br />\n19.06.2020 19:50<br />\n<br />\n國台辦批評台灣的陸委會公布所謂「香港人道援助關懷行動項目」，發言人朱鳳蓮指，再次暴露民進黨當局插手香港事務、破壞香港繁榮穩定的政治圖謀，為黑暴及亂港分子提供庇護並引入島內，只會繼續禍害台灣民眾。她強調，台獨港獨合流破壞一國兩制同分裂國家的圖謀絕不會得逞。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會主委陳明通昨日表示，將在台港策進會下特別成立對外窗口，建立台港服務交流辦公室，下月1日營運，為港人提供赴台就學、就業、投資創業、移民定居等服務；同時在兼顧台灣安全前提下，依據既有法律及公私協力的管道，務實處理港人人道援助及關懷事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1314176&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1314176%26csid%3D261_341&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C3HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=79c45ae4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1314176&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"29edb3e28389b8bdaf6d2a21a27ec152a26aa175","tid":2070880,"uid":29836,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c169461eec77aed3dd4bd0c92f8b0a9b3be7b6","tid":2070880,"uid":18867,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"咁又點呀 打我阿笨"},{"pid":"8c8a44834e5ee015edbcf1608fe037fa11732063","tid":2070880,"uid":21545,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"English: 敵反我擁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2814fa6959588900b5ff4f080112bf6b9e43c36","tid":2070880,"uid":58209,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"同印度開拖未？"},{"pid":"eb3dceeda508